```plantuml
@startuml Resurgence-VM-Development_Resurgence

package "Resurgence VM" {
    [Virtual Machine Core] as VMCore
    [Bytecode Handling] as Bytecode
    [FFI (Foreign Function Interface)] as FFI
    [Instruction Set] as InstructionSet
    [Error Handling] as ErrorHandling
    [Code Generation] as CodeGen
}

package "External Interfaces" {
    [C/C++ Applications] as CApp
    [Rust Applications] as RustApp
}

VMCore --> Bytecode : reads/writes
VMCore --> InstructionSet : executes
VMCore --> ErrorHandling : reports errors
VMCore --> CodeGen : generates
VMCore --> FFI : provides interface

FFI --> CApp : interacts via\nresurgence.h
FFI --> RustApp : direct integration

Bytecode --> CodeGen : generates
Bytecode --> InstructionSet : contains

ErrorHandling --> VMCore : provides context
ErrorHandling --> FFI : error reporting

@enduml
```